Finding a home has never been easier than with IMMOVLAN, your mobile application for real estate! Discover close to 130,000 properties available throughout Belgium and Europe thanks to this easy and intuitive application. 

With the help of your application, you can virtually visit the houses and flats in your favourite neighbourhoods based on the immersive photos presented and organise your searches thanks to the registration and management functionalities of your favourite properties. The IMMOVLAN application is the easiest way to obtain real estate information in real time wherever you are! 
What are the functionalities of the application? 
- The discovery of all types of property for sale or to rent: houses, flats, plots of land, investment properties, new buildings, town houses, garages, offices, shops and co-owing properties;
- The efficient and fast selection of your favourite properties;
- The complete description of each property with photos, price, surface area, EPC indication, agency references and all useful information to contact the agency. 
- The creation of alerts and push notifications for all new properties on the market;
- The automatic sorting of your searches according to the various filters proposed: postcode, number of rooms, type of property, price range and distance. 

Thank you for using our IMMOVLAN application and we hope that it will meet all your expectations.
The Immovlan team
